sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuario
    participant B as Browser
    participant N as NextAuth
    participant G as Google OAuth
    participant GW as Gateway
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>B: Clic "Continuar con Google"
    B->>N: signIn("google")
    N->>G: Redirect a consent screen
    G-->>U: Pantalla de permisos
    U->>G: Autoriza
    G-->>N: id_token + access_token + refresh_token

    Note over N: JWT Callback (server-side)
    N->>GW: POST /auth/verify {id_token}
    GW->>G: Valida id_token con Google
    G-->>GW: OK (sub, email)
    GW->>DB: Upsert usuario (user_id = Google sub)
    GW-->>N: {user_id: "google_sub_123"}

    Note over N: Session Callback
    N->>N: session.user_id = user_id
    N->>N: session.emailHash = SHA256(email)
    N->>N: session.isAdmin = (email === ADMIN_EMAIL)
    N-->>B: Set-Cookie: next-auth.session-token (300s)

    B-->>U: Redirect a /chat

    Note over U,B: Enviar mensaje al chat
    U->>B: Escribe pregunta y envía
    B->>B: POST /api/chat {message}
    Note over B: Next.js server proxy
    B->>B: getServerSession() → extrae id_token
    B->>GW: POST /api/chat {message}<br/>Authorization: Bearer id_token<br/>X-API-Key: gk_web_...<br/>X-Real-IP: client_ip
    GW-->>B: {reply, sources, warnings}
    B-->>U: Muestra respuesta con Voti
